<tr id="L29"><td><a href="#L29">29</a></td><td>NEELIX:  That's odd.</td></tr>

<tr id="L30"><td><a href="#L30">30</a></td><td>TUVOK [OC]:  I'm detecting</td></tr>

<tr><td></td><td>LOCATION--Delta Flyer - aft section</td></tr>
