<tr id="L112"><td><a href="#L112">112</a></td><td>EMH:  Relax, Commander, I only want to scan you.</td></tr>

<tr id="L113"><td><a href="#L113">113</a></td><td>NEELIX:  Don't worry, Tuvok, he's only trying to help you. It's only a tricorder. See? It won't hurt you.</td></tr>

